creator: MENUPAY
descriptionHtml:
Welcome to the new MENUPAY! New logo, new app and a lot of new features!
MENUPAY is a restaurant program, that gives up to 30% discount on the entire bill, when you pay with this app. MENUPAY has agreements with over 500 restaurants in Denmark, ranging from Michelin restaurants to coffee shops and sushi places.

MENUPAY has a user-friendly search function and provides you with a quick overview of the different restaurant options as well as current discounts.

It is now much simpler to complete a payment: fewer steps and a light background which makes it easier to read the screen in the dark restaurants.

When you are ready to pay, choose ‘Pay’, find your restaurant in the app and enter the full amount (the discount will be shown in the app and deducted before your payment). Inform the staff that you would like to pay with MENUPAY, when you are about to pay.

With the MENUPAY app you can:
• Pay quickly and safely with the app – your payment details are encrypted and safely stored with QuickPay
• Add several payment cards and name them
• Enjoy a user-friendly search function: search on name, city or street
• Get an overview of all restaurants on a map
• See the restaurants’ menu
• Change your profile details
• Access your old receipts
• Add a photo or a note to your receipt when you pay with MENUPAY
• Use biometric access (fingerprint and face recognition) to approve your payments
• Buy gift cards to MENUPAY
• Use our Event Service to plan your next company event
• See current campaigns, Dining Days and news



Please be aware that you need to sign up before you get the benefits of the MENUPAY app. You can sign up through your employer, if they have an agreement with MENUPAY.
If you experience any problems with the app or have any general feedback, feel free to contact us at
kontakt@menupay.com

Please be aware that the use of location services can shorten the batteries lifespan.

title: MenuPay

creator: MENUPAY
descriptionHtml:
With MENUPAY you and your colleagues get up to 30% discount and special offers at restaurants, cafés, brasseries, bakeries, and bars in Denmark – both when dining out or when ordering your favourite takeaway. MENUPAY is a simple payment solution that you use when dining at restaurants. MENUPAY is 100% free to use and provides you with lots of inspiration.


To access and enjoy all the benefits, your employer should sign a company agreement with MENUPAY. The agreement is non-binding and at no cost. Your workplace can sign up here: https://menupay.com/en/sign-up-as-a-company.


If your workplace already has an agreement with MENUPAY, simply download the MENUPAY app, sign up with a SIGN-UP code provided by your employer and start saving now. You can use MENUPAY both for private and business dining.


Still not sure if MENUPAY is something for you and your workplace? Try the app with our 30-day free trial. Simply download the app, follow the instructions and prepare yourself for fantastic dining experiences and great discounts, in only two minutes.


MENUPAY offers:
• Access to everything from Michelin restaurants to well-known fast food chains
• Up to 30% discount on both restaurant dining and takeaway
• Easy, safe, and quick payment through the app
• All receipts in one place
• Gift cards that can be used at more than 450 restaurants
• Inspiration for your next dining
… and much more!


Any questions about registration, the 30-day trial, the app itself or anything else? Feel free to contact our customer service by phone or e-mail:
• E-mail: kontakt@menupay.com
• Phone: +45 3131 6464

Welcome to your future favourite app and bon appétit.

Please be aware that the use of location services can shorten the batteries lifespan.

• Contact us, FAQ and Introduction have moved to profile for your convenience
• Other minor bug fixes and improvements
